  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Buffet Breakfast </strong>with a selection of fresh pastries, bread, cheeses, meats, cereal, fruit, fresh fruit juice, teas and coffee and hot options including scrambled eggs is served in the Breakfast room. Guests can have breakfast out on the terrace beside the pool in the warmer weather.</p>
<p>Half board options are available for a supplement.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
