  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><u>Restaurants &amp; Bars </u></strong></p>
<p><strong>The Abbots Court </strong>Enjoy the culinary creations of our chefs, steeped in Sicilian tradition and made using the finest fresh produce, from the properties very own vegetable gardens where possible. On each table you’ll fine a bottle of the properties home made olive oil. Choose from the a la carte menu or put your choice in the hands of the excellent chef and choose the tasting menu. In the warmer weather dine al fresco, under the stars in the beautiful cobbled courtyard.</p>
<p><strong>Il Nido del Falco</strong><strong> Bar</strong> is a comfortable lounge bar serving the wine produced at the property as well as other drinks. During the day the bar serves drinks and light snacks that can be enjoyed close to the pool.</p>
<p><strong><u>Pools &amp; Beaches</u></strong></p>
<p><strong>Swimming Pool </strong>Set amidst nature, the large swimming pool with built in hydromassage is surrounded by a sun terrace that looks out towards the Tyrrhenian sea with the Aeolian Islands in the distance. The terrace is equipped with comfortable sun loungers so guests can relax and unwind by the pool.</p>
<p>The swimming pool can be used by guests from May to August, from 9:00am to 1:00pm and from 2:30pm to 7:00pm.</p>
<p><strong>Beaches </strong>Although the hotel is set up in the hills you won’t find yourself far from the clear waters and sandy beaches of the Cefalu coast (approx. 25 minuites)</p>
<p><strong><u>Activities</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Fitness Room equipped with weights and modern gym equipment.</li>
<li>Billiard Room</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><u>General Facilities </u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free wifi in public areas</li>
<li>Parking</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
