  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are between 17-26m² and are all different due to the historic nature of the building. They are furnished in an elegant Madonita style, using rich warm tones. These double rooms can accommodate a third single bed allowing them to sleep up to three people. All rooms are equipped with a desk, satellite TV, telephone, mini-bar, radio, safe, air conditioning, heating, bathroom with shower, hairdryer, towels and bathrobes.</p>
<p><br />Single occupancy rooms, deluxe rooms and suites are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
